data.description: Discover this stunning La Contenta Golf Course home! The spacious living room with beamed ceilings, built-in fireplace & picturesque windows create an inviting ambiance. Enjoy the formal dining area, while the kitchen is an entertainer's delight, complete with a breakfast bar & dining nook. An abundance of kitchen cabinetry offers ample storage, includes a butler's sink, ideal for a coffee bar setup. Discover a built-in lighted desk area thoughtfully integrated within the kitchen. The Master Bathroom is a masterpiece, having undergone a tasteful renovation featuring a beautifully tiled walk-in shower. Stunning landscaping sets the stage, featuring a gazebo nestled over a concrete patio set. Two sheds offer endless possibilities. Side access provides easy accommodation for a Boat/RV. Fully fenced backyard spans a generous half acre with a garden area. Entertain with the expansive decking, shaded by native oaks that bring a touch of serenity to your gatherings. Whether hosting friends or savoring moments of solitude, this outdoor haven offers the best of both worlds. Garage storage with built-in cabinets/shelving and a half-bath add convenience. Don't miss your chance to Love where you Live!
